Some suggestions from your friendly neighborhood fool....<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:yellow;font-family:courier;font-size:large;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Account Preferences</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:red;font-family:courier;font-size:medium;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Is your subject header not filling automatically?</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
<br>
Use the link in the upper left as you're looking at all the forums that's called <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:orange;font-family:courier;">&quot;My control center&quot;</span><!--EZCODE FONT END-->. Then click on <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:orange;font-family:courier;">&quot;Account preferences.&quot;</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--> In account preferences there are alot of options you can include or not. One of them is called <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:orange;font-family:courier;">&quot;Auto fill of subject when replying&quot;</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--> Make sure it's checked. I'd also suggest checking <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:orange;font-family:courier;">&quot;Move updated topics to the top&quot;</span><!--EZCODE FONT END-->, <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:orange;font-family:courier;">&quot;Auto-link URL's&quot;</span><!--EZCODE FONT END-->, and <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:orange;font-family:courier;">&quot;ez codes&quot;.</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:red;font-family:courier;font-size:medium;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Stay in touch!!! </strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> </span><!--EZCODE FONT END--> <br>
<br>
While you're at it check <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:orange;font-family:courier;">&quot;Accept private messages&quot;</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--> and <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:orange;font-family:courier;">&quot;Accept Administrator E-mails&quot;</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--> just for me.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->     <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:red;font-family:courier;font-size:medium;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>High Security</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
<br>
Enabling high security kinda sucks... Leave it off if you don't like logging in constantly.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:red;font-family:courier;font-size:medium;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Signatures</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
<br>
You can also choose to enable signatures and personal icon URL's. The personal Icon URL is the tiny square next to some people's names.<br>
<br>
Also...<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:yellow;font-family:courier;font-size:large;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Public Profile</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:red;font-family:courier;font-size:medium;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Avatars</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
<br>
Use the link in the upper left as you're looking at all the forums that's called <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:orange;font-family:courier;">&quot;My control center&quot;</span><!--EZCODE FONT END-->.  Then click on <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:orange;font-family:courier;">&quot;public profile&quot;</span><!--EZCODE FONT END-->.   If you want an avatar make sure that the privacy button is not on next to <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:orange;font-family:courier;">&quot;My photo&quot;</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--> and enter the URL of the picture.  Whether you want your name and birth date seen is up to you, check the box if you don't want anyone that's curious to see these things.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:red;font-family:courier;font-size:medium;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Optional fields</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
