<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:red;font-family:courier;font-size:medium;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>E-mail and self promotion</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END-->  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
