The buttons below the post window are <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:orange;font-family:courier;">&quot;custom signature&quot;</span><!--EZCODE FONT END-->, <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:orange;font-family:courier;">&quot;Include personal photo&quot;</span><!--EZCODE FONT END-->, <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:orange;font-family:courier;">&quot;Convert URL links&quot;</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--> and<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:orange;font-family:courier;"> &quot;e-mail notification of all replies&quot;</span><!--EZCODE FONT END-->.  I have the first 3 checked because I hate spammed mail boxes.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->     <br>
<br>
If you are missing a sig or an avatar, check these boxes.<br>
<br>
I'll most likely be adding to this as more questions arise.<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:orange;font-size:large;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Before any of these changes take effect you must post.  The changes are not retroactive.  Your previous Avatars will be unaffected.</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:orange;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>New....</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:yellow;font-family:courier;font-size:large;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Navigation</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
<br>
The best easiest way to navigate without missing any posts is this...<br>
<br>
Read and post in the messages that you have an interest in.  Look to see that no one has posted behind you.  Read the name of the last poster in the topic selection view and if the top non-sticky subjects aren't your name then someone has posted behind you. (this will happen alot on the Observation Deck)  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    <br>
<br>
When you've read the threads you want to read click on the tab near the top of the screen that says <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:orange;font-family:courier;">&quot;Mark topic in this forum as read&quot;</span><!--EZCODE FONT END-->.  Click it.  It will reset all the pips (the little dull yellow markers to the left of the topic and the forum that indicate new posts) and it will send you out to choose another forum.<br>
<br>
Go to the next forum you're interested in that has a pip next to it and repeat the above procedure.<br>
<br>
This way you won't miss any new posts and it makes navigation alot easier.<br>
